86,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:21:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d550493174bc13a38cc09bff950092baf27504d","tid":1515013,"uid":190847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:48:53.000Z","msg":"down左唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a573a72f88c52342da73dba72df191532cbbc1da","tid":1515013,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2aaa5ad90cf0cfe1e55e9450d9d8c2f9376e4a6","tid":1515013,"uid":241869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1dd140d286b616ced8af7cbf8d0d49c431b0e7b2","tid":1515013,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:31:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b87bcb17804d0e5a8679bf3bdab022edbdf1c98","tid":1515013,"uid":60005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:35:17.000Z","msg":"無人用的 次次都唔見有人講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae842501cd1ffacf9ed5ef4466e272817d0b92f","tid":1515013,"uid":63314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:39:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2b4ee34cfc055731a1059870180837f412dbfb3b","tid":1515013,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8128a2833ef4a91be3302ada65721bb6da688e2","tid":1515013,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"無懼緊急法封網絡，每人手機成就藍芽網絡，保持抗爭資訊流通!<br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考返之前既POST:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n【突發！！！】Bridgefy公開支持香港示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1482449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1482449</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Bridgefy</strong> 有 4 種使用模式，能因應沒網路的「非常時期」<br />\n<br />\n(1) 人-人模式（PERSON TO PERSON MODE）<br />\n<br />\n在這種模式下，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">只要打開藍牙</span></strong>就能與距離使用者不到 100 公尺的朋友進行私聊。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以即時召集當區手足, 聚集, 再一齊行動/出發</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(2) 網狀網路模式（MESH MODE）<br />\n<br />\n在 MESH MODE 下，可以透過中間點（另一名 Bridgefy 使用者）與超過 100 公尺以外的朋友聊天，也就是呈現<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">【人 1-人 2-人 3】的傳訊模式</span></strong>，使可能通訊距離達到 200 公尺， 人 1 與人 3 之間的訊息將維持私密性，人 2 是無法閱讀其訊息的。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">需要多人使用，組成藍芽網絡，越多人網絡越廣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(3) 廣播模式（BROADCAST MODE）<br />\n<br />\n在廣播模式下，使用者可以<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">同時向周圍所有使用 Bridgefy 的人發送訊息</span></strong>，即使這些人並不在聯絡人列表中。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以行動中宣佈重大決定時用</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(4) 線上模式（ONLINE MODE）<br />\n<br />\n除了這三種模式以外，Bridgefy 也有 online 模式可以使用，可以透過網路連接到所有有使用 Bridgefy ，並同樣是以網路連線的朋友們。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔好只係自己DOWN, 要傳開去, 連登以外既人!!<br />\n一定要盡快一人一APP, 已經有傳831可以推緊急法<br />\n唔好鬆懈!<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:41:12.000Z","msg":"希望今日香港中區無暴徒出現啦<br />\n要暴去其他地區咪仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b718cd4a2e9d9afaa5d9e691723bccedbb8f3e","tid":1515013,"uid":26557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}